{"type":null,"faqId":44739,"title":"天气时钟使用方法","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">在桌面预置的Widget（桌面小工具）中已经包含天气时钟，点击小工具，可以打开天气时钟。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">左右滑动可以查看不同城市的天气状态。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">刷新：按住屏幕下拉，可以刷新数据。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">城市管理：点击添加城市，可以添加成功；已有的城市，长按可以删除该城市天气显示。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">          点击管理城市界面下方的设置，进入设置界面，可以设置 天气时钟的温度单位和是否显示声音，更新时间等。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"240","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409159000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":6,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"天气时钟","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}